'''David Leopold Affengruber''' (born 19 March 2001) is an Austrian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for {{Spanish football updater|Elche}} club [[Elche CF|Elche]] and the [[Austria national football team|Austria national team]].

==Club career==
Affengruber began his career at SC Wieselburg. In September 2013 he moved to the youth team of [[FC Red Bull Salzburg|Red Bull Salzburg]]. From the 2015–16 season he played in all age groups in the academy at Red Bull Salzburg.

For the 2019–20 season he was promoted to [[FC Liefering]]. He made his debut for Liefering in the second division in July 2019. He started against [[SKU Amstetten]] on matchday one of that season. In the game he also scored his first second division goal.

In January 2021 he made his Bundesliga debut for Red Bull Salzburg against [[TSV Hartberg]]. In February 2021 he received a contract in Salzburg that ran until May 2022.<ref>[https://www.redbullsalzburg.at/de/fc-red-bull-salzburg/news/saison_2020_21/neuer-vertrag-fuer-david-affengruber.html FC Red Bull Salzburg Homepage]</ref> By the end of the season he had made five appearances for Salzburg in the Bundesliga.

On 11 June 2021, Affengruber signed a three-year contract with [[SK Sturm Graz|Sturm Graz]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[SK Sturm Graz|Sturm Graz]]|url=https://www.sksturm.at/de/news/kampfmannschaft/2021/sturm-graz-verpflichtet-david-affengruber/|title=STURM GRAZ VERPFLICHTET DAVID AFFENGRUBER|date=11 June 2021|language=de|access-date=11 June 2021|archive-date=11 January 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220111182131/https://www.sksturm.at/de/news/kampfmannschaft/2021/sturm-graz-verpflichtet-david-affengruber/|url-status=dead}}</ref> On 28 August 2024, he moved abroad for the first time in his career after joining Spanish [[Segunda División]] side [[Elche CF|Elche]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.elchecf.es/noticias/affengruber-un-refuerzo-de-lujo-para-cerrar-la-defensa-del-elche-cf|title=Affengruber, un refuerzo de lujo para cerrar la defensa del Elche CF|trans-title=Affengruber, a luxury signing to complete the defense of Elche CF|publisher=Elche CF|language=es|date=28 August 2024|accessdate=28 August 2024}}</ref>

==International career==
Affengruber made his debut for the Austrian U-19 team against Latvia in September 2019. He made his U-21 debut against [[Norway national under-21 football team|Norway]] in September 2021.

